WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.861
=Episode 23=

01:48.048 --> 01:48.944
Come in.

01:50.545 --> 01:51.985
Ms. Xu, here's our latest

01:51.985 --> 01:53.265
sample video feedback report.

01:53.265 --> 01:54.105
Take a look.

01:54.944 --> 01:56.224
We'll ship the goods next week.

01:56.385 --> 01:58.960
Focus on customer reviews
and after-sales issues.

01:58.960 --> 01:59.944
Got it.

02:00.344 --> 02:00.944
Go ahead.

02:00.944 --> 02:01.465
Alright.

02:19.424 --> 02:20.464
Hello, Ms. Song.

02:21.385 --> 02:22.505
Did anything go wrong

02:22.505 --> 02:23.864
with Haochen at school?

02:25.505 --> 02:26.024
No.

02:26.424 --> 02:27.985
Haochen's doing well.

02:29.904 --> 02:30.985
Do you have a minute?

02:33.424 --> 02:33.945
Yeah.

02:34.065 --> 02:35.624
It's Parents' Day next Saturday.

02:35.704 --> 02:36.385
Got it.

02:36.972 --> 02:39.192
(Relationship Guide, Real-World Clarity)

02:41.864 --> 02:42.584
Brother-in-law.

02:43.265 --> 02:44.385
Interesting paragraph.

02:45.704 --> 02:47.304
Even for a married couple,

02:48.024 --> 02:50.304
what keeps the marriage alive

02:50.304 --> 02:51.304
isn't the certificate

02:52.024 --> 02:54.065
or how much they sacrifice

02:54.545 --> 02:55.545
for the relationship.

02:56.265 --> 02:57.624
What really binds them

02:57.624 --> 03:01.265
is their ability
to maintain the relationship

03:01.665 --> 03:03.105
and resolve conflicts.

03:05.345 --> 03:06.545
This is profound.

03:07.225 --> 03:08.584
It requires deep thought.

03:11.265 --> 03:12.144
Enjoy.

03:12.225 --> 03:12.825
Thank you.

03:16.184 --> 03:17.665
I know the theory,

03:17.665 --> 03:19.424
but what should I do?

03:22.985 --> 03:23.704
Listen to this.

03:24.945 --> 03:27.304
World Literary Masters on Love.

03:28.105 --> 03:29.584
Maugham said,

03:30.265 --> 03:31.785
"In matters of love,

03:32.184 --> 03:34.065
if you consider self-esteem,

03:34.345 --> 03:35.505
the only explanation

03:35.744 --> 03:38.184
is that you've only
ever loved yourself."

03:38.424 --> 03:38.985
Therefore,

03:39.505 --> 03:40.665
if you really love her

03:40.945 --> 03:41.825
and want her back,

03:42.545 --> 03:45.385
you should completely discard your pride

03:45.744 --> 03:46.624
and take initiative.

03:47.105 --> 03:47.744
Be fearless.

03:47.945 --> 03:48.904
Be shameless.

03:49.665 --> 03:50.704
Don't be afraid

03:51.505 --> 03:52.545
to embarrass yourself.

04:00.105 --> 04:01.105
Are you free tomorrow?

04:01.265 --> 04:02.225
Meet me at the cafÃ©.

04:02.505 --> 04:03.545
It's about Haochen.

04:06.624 --> 04:08.265
We can meet tomorrow. I...

04:08.704 --> 04:09.345
Don't.

04:09.945 --> 04:10.665
Don't send it.

04:10.825 --> 04:11.345
Wait.

04:13.144 --> 04:14.345
Not tomorrow.

04:14.985 --> 04:15.624
Today.

04:15.945 --> 04:16.624
Go to her place.

04:20.304 --> 04:22.025
You came here fast.

04:26.944 --> 04:27.785
Why are you here?

04:28.465 --> 04:29.624
Didn't we agree to

04:29.624 --> 04:31.184
meet at the cafÃ© tomorrow?

04:32.145 --> 04:34.304
I happened to have a meeting nearby.

04:34.585 --> 04:36.585
So I thought I'd drop by

04:36.744 --> 04:38.465
and ask about Haochen.

04:39.064 --> 04:39.905
May I come in?

04:40.985 --> 04:41.824
Shoes off?

04:42.608 --> 04:43.384
No need.

04:50.785 --> 04:51.785
It's Parents' Day

04:51.785 --> 04:53.624
next week at Haochen's school.

04:54.264 --> 04:56.585
The parent organizing this time

04:56.585 --> 04:59.025
wants me to share our last event's plan.

04:59.264 --> 05:01.705
But I've been swamped with work.

05:02.105 --> 05:03.184
And I can't reach her.

05:03.465 --> 05:05.145
I'll send you the documents.

05:05.264 --> 05:06.504
Contact her, okay?

05:08.585 --> 05:09.744
You're having guests?

05:10.384 --> 05:11.545
I sent you the link.

05:11.624 --> 05:12.585
Did you get it?

05:14.105 --> 05:15.025
Just download it.

05:15.120 --> 05:15.792
Okay.

05:19.665 --> 05:20.345
Received it?

05:23.665 --> 05:24.384
Poor connection.

05:25.985 --> 05:27.025
Do you have Wi-Fi here?

05:28.705 --> 05:31.585
My router's broken.
Download it when you get home.

05:31.585 --> 05:32.905
Let me fix it for you.

05:33.624 --> 05:34.785
I've scheduled a repair.

05:34.785 --> 05:36.345
I got this. It'll be quick.

05:36.424 --> 05:37.304
I'll fix it.

05:42.424 --> 05:43.465
T-Thank you.

05:45.624 --> 05:46.785
It just needs a reboot.

05:51.184 --> 05:51.824
Okay.

05:52.864 --> 05:53.424
Yan.

05:53.905 --> 05:55.905
What's your Wi-Fi password?

05:55.985 --> 05:57.145
My phone number.

05:57.145 --> 05:57.744
Okay.

05:58.105 --> 05:59.145
- 100.
- 100...

05:59.585 --> 06:02.985
51807561.

06:03.785 --> 06:04.304
Let's see.

06:09.064 --> 06:09.944
Still not working.

06:11.864 --> 06:12.905
Do you have a modem?

06:12.944 --> 06:13.465
Where is it?

06:16.145 --> 06:17.744
Just download it at home.

06:17.944 --> 06:19.025
It'll be quick.

06:19.345 --> 06:20.064
Where's the modem?

06:20.864 --> 06:23.864
The modem is in the shoe cabinet.

06:23.864 --> 06:24.545
Got it.

06:24.905 --> 06:25.744
Go ahead.

06:33.545 --> 06:34.184
Found it.

06:45.304 --> 06:46.944
Let's see the living room signal.

06:49.145 --> 06:49.905
It's good now.

06:52.665 --> 06:54.744
Mind if I check your bedroom

06:55.304 --> 06:56.545
for the signal?

06:57.304 --> 06:57.864
Go ahead.

07:00.465 --> 07:01.064
Yan.

07:01.064 --> 07:02.585
Do you mind if I close the door?

07:04.025 --> 07:05.304
It's more accurate.

07:06.585 --> 07:07.264
It'll be quick.

07:08.705 --> 07:09.384
Alright.

07:42.345 --> 07:43.312
Looking for something?

07:48.345 --> 07:52.345
Good signal under and above the bed.

07:53.864 --> 07:54.785
Full coverage.

07:56.184 --> 07:56.905
The bathroom.

08:05.465 --> 08:07.785
Perfect.

08:07.824 --> 08:08.345
Finally,

08:08.424 --> 08:09.145
by the window.

08:14.905 --> 08:16.225
You have full coverage now.

08:16.824 --> 08:17.665
That's great.

08:18.665 --> 08:19.864
Thank you so much.

08:21.025 --> 08:24.304
Go back and check the documents.

08:27.184 --> 08:28.145
I'll get going then.

08:28.824 --> 08:29.465
Bye.

08:31.985 --> 08:33.144
These curtains...

08:33.144 --> 08:33.664
No.

08:33.784 --> 08:35.225
I-I can change them myself.

08:35.345 --> 08:36.504
It's fine. I'll help you.

08:36.864 --> 08:39.225
It's dangerous and tiring for girls.

08:39.225 --> 08:40.504
You don't have to do this.

08:40.504 --> 08:41.465
It's okay. I got this.

08:44.752 --> 08:45.744
Shen Haoming.

08:46.504 --> 08:47.544
Smells amazing.

08:48.144 --> 08:49.185
What soup are you making?

08:50.264 --> 08:51.144
Coconut chicken soup.

08:52.345 --> 08:53.384
Careful there.

08:58.305 --> 08:59.945
This is your signature soup.

09:16.985 --> 09:18.744
Must be an important guest.

09:25.465 --> 09:26.264
Yan, look.

09:26.904 --> 09:27.744
Smooth, right?

09:31.144 --> 09:32.705
Thanks. You've worked hard today.

09:34.264 --> 09:35.024
My pleasure.

09:47.744 --> 09:49.392
You cooked quite a feast today.

09:55.624 --> 09:56.585
It's already dark.

09:56.624 --> 09:57.544
Head back home.

09:58.024 --> 09:59.504
Pay more attention to Haochen.

09:59.544 --> 10:00.864
Ask me if you need help.

10:01.225 --> 10:01.784
Alright then.

10:02.864 --> 10:03.784
I'll go back now.

10:06.544 --> 10:08.705
Call me if your Wi-Fi ever fails again.

10:08.904 --> 10:09.985
Okay. Thanks.

10:15.144 --> 10:16.144
Finally here.

10:16.264 --> 10:17.024
What did you say?

10:17.904 --> 10:19.024
Your guest has arrived.

10:21.585 --> 10:22.225
Go ahead.

10:22.784 --> 10:23.544
I'll get the door.

10:27.345 --> 10:28.225
Shen Haoming?

10:28.816 --> 10:29.624
Sister.

10:30.185 --> 10:31.144
Long time no see.

10:31.504 --> 10:32.504
Come on in.

10:35.425 --> 10:35.985
Yao.

10:36.305 --> 10:36.904
Guan.

10:37.624 --> 10:38.225
Hello.

10:38.465 --> 10:39.345
I'm Shen Haoming.

10:43.185 --> 10:43.945
Don't stand there.

10:43.985 --> 10:44.585
Come in.

10:44.904 --> 10:45.624
Keep the shoes on.

10:53.904 --> 10:54.465
Yan.

10:54.784 --> 10:55.544
I brought fruits.

10:55.825 --> 10:56.264
Yan.

10:56.496 --> 10:57.105
A cake for you.

10:57.105 --> 10:57.744
Thank you.

10:57.784 --> 10:58.384
Thank you.

11:00.225 --> 11:00.825
Sit.

11:01.904 --> 11:03.185
I'll get you some drinks.

11:06.985 --> 11:08.065
What are you doing?

11:10.504 --> 11:11.864
Your sister and besties are here.

11:12.105 --> 11:13.264
We should treat them well.

11:14.024 --> 11:14.705
Shen Haoming.

11:20.825 --> 11:21.384
Is this okay?

11:21.465 --> 11:22.465
Okay, thanks.

11:22.864 --> 11:23.465
What happened?

11:23.825 --> 11:24.624
Why is he here?

11:25.425 --> 11:26.024
No idea.

11:26.985 --> 11:28.144
He fixed the router

11:28.585 --> 11:30.024
and changed the curtains.

11:31.065 --> 11:32.425
I don't know why he won't leave.

11:32.705 --> 11:33.585
He won't leave?

11:34.425 --> 11:35.384
Okay, let him stay.

11:36.065 --> 11:37.065
Let me handle this.

11:45.225 --> 11:48.225
Thank you for taking care of Yan

11:48.624 --> 11:49.904
this whole time.

11:51.624 --> 11:53.065
You've worked hard

11:53.585 --> 11:55.065
and achieved such great results

11:55.105 --> 11:56.384
in such a short time.

11:56.705 --> 11:57.945
As her husband,

11:58.544 --> 12:00.225
I'm really proud.

12:00.825 --> 12:02.345
It's such a nice opportunity

12:02.345 --> 12:04.504
to meet you and hang out here.

12:09.985 --> 12:10.784
Annoying ex.

12:10.784 --> 12:12.024
Why is he texting me again?

12:12.024 --> 12:12.904
So annoying.

12:13.065 --> 12:13.784
Unbelievable.

12:15.585 --> 12:16.664
You haven't blocked him?

12:21.705 --> 12:24.425
She shouldn't just delete his contact.

12:24.585 --> 12:26.624
She should curse him every now and then,

12:26.744 --> 12:27.425
block him,

12:28.225 --> 12:29.664
unblock him after some time,

12:29.744 --> 12:30.624
curse him again,

12:30.864 --> 12:31.504
and block him.

12:32.504 --> 12:34.225
That's what he deserves.

12:35.585 --> 12:37.305
Some men are just like that.

12:37.544 --> 12:39.624
When someone is in love with them,

12:39.784 --> 12:40.784
they take it for granted.

12:41.345 --> 12:42.544
But when that love fades,

12:43.024 --> 12:44.504
they suddenly can't let go.

12:45.305 --> 12:46.744
Aren't they mentally ill?

12:46.985 --> 12:48.024
Yes, they are.

12:48.305 --> 12:50.105
Those people are abnormal.

12:52.585 --> 12:54.065
Don't be afraid...

12:54.105 --> 12:55.225
To embarrass yourself.

12:56.784 --> 12:58.425
Let's play a game.

12:58.624 --> 12:59.784
Use two-word phrases

12:59.784 --> 13:00.705
to describe our exes.

13:00.705 --> 13:01.264
Okay?

13:01.705 --> 13:02.705
I'll go first.

13:03.185 --> 13:04.465
Stubborn fool.

13:05.384 --> 13:06.664
Blind idiot.

13:06.985 --> 13:08.065
Calculating brat.

13:08.504 --> 13:09.185
One more.

13:09.784 --> 13:10.624
Ungrateful wretch.

13:11.185 --> 13:11.945
Nice.

13:12.144 --> 13:14.305
So how should we treat them?

13:14.384 --> 13:15.624
Obviously,

13:15.904 --> 13:18.305
leave them to die alone.

13:18.945 --> 13:19.945
Destitute in old age.

13:21.384 --> 13:22.784
And what kind of attitude

13:22.784 --> 13:24.024
should we adopt?

13:25.305 --> 13:26.504
Ignore them.

13:27.784 --> 13:30.024
Act like they're dead.

13:32.705 --> 13:33.225
Oh right,

13:33.784 --> 13:35.544
Jinda Group's new mall

13:35.585 --> 13:37.504
is opening soon.

13:38.465 --> 13:40.144
Feel free to visit.

13:40.544 --> 13:42.585
Buy whatever you like.

13:43.384 --> 13:44.384
My treat.

13:45.024 --> 13:45.825
Your treat?

13:49.425 --> 13:50.504
How much discount?

13:51.264 --> 13:51.825
All for free.

13:56.024 --> 13:59.945
My secretary will go with you.

14:02.185 --> 14:04.744
Mr. Shen is absolutely

14:05.305 --> 14:06.345
approachable.

14:06.904 --> 14:07.945
Confident and kind.

14:08.664 --> 14:09.784
Peerlessly handsome.

14:10.225 --> 14:11.465
A true gentleman.

14:19.624 --> 14:21.065
Showing off your vocabulary?

14:21.664 --> 14:23.105
You know so many phrases, huh?

14:23.264 --> 14:24.825
Ms. Xu is cooking alone.

14:24.825 --> 14:25.864
Won't you help her?

14:26.065 --> 14:26.664
Yeah.

14:27.664 --> 14:28.345
- I forgot.
- Hurry.

14:28.465 --> 14:29.105
Let's help her.

14:29.105 --> 14:29.585
Let's go.

14:29.744 --> 14:30.945
Ms. Xu.

14:31.504 --> 14:32.024
Ms. Xu.

14:32.425 --> 14:33.384
Ms. Xu.

14:33.425 --> 14:34.384
Let us do this.

14:34.585 --> 14:35.024
Ms. Xu.

14:35.024 --> 14:35.744
Take a break.

14:35.784 --> 14:36.544
Rest for a bit.

14:36.585 --> 14:37.585
We've got this.

14:43.744 --> 14:45.185
Why don't you go home?

14:45.465 --> 14:47.585
It's your first time
attending Parents' Day.

14:47.585 --> 14:49.305
There is a lot to do.

14:50.065 --> 14:50.705
It's fine.

14:51.225 --> 14:52.705
Let me talk with Lin a bit more.

14:52.825 --> 14:54.000
I have nothing to say to you.

14:56.784 --> 14:57.504
Alright.

14:58.345 --> 14:59.144
Then I'm off.

15:00.384 --> 15:01.465
Call me if you need help

15:02.024 --> 15:03.056
with your Wi-Fi.

15:05.784 --> 15:06.345
Ladies,

15:06.825 --> 15:09.185
Jinda Mall welcomes you anytime.

15:10.345 --> 15:11.105
Thanks, Mr. Shen.

15:11.345 --> 15:12.225
Bye, Mr. Shen.

15:19.472 --> 15:21.784
He acted like the host here.

15:23.065 --> 15:23.945
So shameless.

15:24.065 --> 15:24.945
I don't get it.

15:25.345 --> 15:25.985
Forget it.

15:26.800 --> 15:28.065
Come on, let's eat.

15:28.504 --> 15:29.264
Let's eat.

15:29.305 --> 15:30.024
Set the table.

15:30.024 --> 15:31.185
You have the appetite?

15:32.705 --> 15:33.705
What happened just now?

15:34.065 --> 15:35.985
You betrayed your friend

15:36.065 --> 15:37.144
for some petty money?

15:38.384 --> 15:39.024
Brother-in-law.

15:40.264 --> 15:41.504
Why does the drink

15:42.345 --> 15:43.264
taste so bitter today?

15:49.664 --> 15:50.352
Brother-in-law.

15:51.504 --> 15:53.985
Your sadness and sorrow
have been transmitted

15:54.544 --> 15:55.544
to the brain,

15:56.504 --> 15:59.024
which then signals the glands.

16:00.225 --> 16:02.425
These glands received neural stimulation

16:03.065 --> 16:04.345
and secreted melatonin,

16:05.144 --> 16:06.105
causing low mood.

16:06.105 --> 16:06.904
It's normal.

16:08.784 --> 16:10.624
Just take some Vitamin B.

16:14.185 --> 16:14.705
Yeah.

16:16.345 --> 16:18.384
My previous advice was wrong.

16:19.705 --> 16:20.345
As you know,

16:20.945 --> 16:23.105
we doctors have
multiple treatment plans.

16:25.825 --> 16:27.185
There's a Plan B?

16:27.544 --> 16:28.144
Of course.

16:28.425 --> 16:29.305
(Excerpt)
Your longing,

16:30.624 --> 16:31.425
your regrets,

16:32.225 --> 16:33.225
and your anguish

16:34.985 --> 16:36.504
should all be shown to them.

16:37.185 --> 16:38.504
As they say, "When a man cries,

16:38.504 --> 16:39.624
a woman's heart softens."

16:41.345 --> 16:44.624
The second tactic is to be love-sick.

16:51.408 --> 16:54.161
(Yan Studio)

17:00.024 --> 17:00.945
What brings you here?

17:02.384 --> 17:02.985
Thanks.

17:04.784 --> 17:05.385
Yan.

17:06.504 --> 17:07.945
I thought about it a lot

17:08.225 --> 17:09.264
and decided that

17:09.465 --> 17:11.024
you should know about this.

17:12.824 --> 17:13.504
Look.

17:16.185 --> 17:16.945
What is this?

17:24.064 --> 17:26.465
These are candid shots I took.

17:30.625 --> 17:31.784
When you were away,

17:32.465 --> 17:33.744
he often visited your building.

17:34.784 --> 17:36.225
Many times, he almost went up,

17:38.344 --> 17:39.504
but always gave up.

18:07.024 --> 18:08.344
And he's been staring

18:09.344 --> 18:10.625
out of the windows at work.

18:14.544 --> 18:15.465
There's more.

18:16.064 --> 18:16.945
When he was sent

18:16.945 --> 18:18.185
to a regional subsidiary,

18:18.905 --> 18:20.264
I secretly took some photos.

18:22.504 --> 18:23.705
The local manager

18:24.145 --> 18:26.665
picked on him to block his audit.

18:27.985 --> 18:29.225
Mr. Shen fought alone

18:29.225 --> 18:30.465
in unfamiliar territory.

18:32.665 --> 18:34.344
What got him through the nights?

18:34.705 --> 18:35.824
Your photos.

18:39.504 --> 18:40.225
Yan.

18:41.225 --> 18:42.544
I can tell

18:43.304 --> 18:44.544
that you're everything

18:44.705 --> 18:46.185
to Mr. Shen.

18:48.784 --> 18:49.985
I haven't seen him smile

18:52.064 --> 18:53.665
for a long time since you left.

18:56.104 --> 18:58.344
You're really important to him.

19:09.504 --> 19:10.264
I see.

19:12.385 --> 19:13.784
The photos are well taken

19:14.465 --> 19:15.425
and clear.

19:15.544 --> 19:16.225
Good work.

19:16.945 --> 19:18.385
I just want to know

19:19.385 --> 19:21.304
what kind of candid shots
could get this close?

19:22.584 --> 19:24.504
Shen Haoming seemed quite cooperative.

19:26.705 --> 19:27.425
And this one.

19:29.425 --> 19:30.784
He was in bed, right?

19:31.544 --> 19:32.225
Yeah.

19:32.385 --> 19:33.744
So you were in bed too?

19:35.425 --> 19:37.344
Both of you were in bed?

19:42.705 --> 19:43.945
Why are you having water?

19:45.504 --> 19:46.665
Why are you nervous?

19:46.665 --> 19:48.264
I get nervous when you're nervous.

19:51.145 --> 19:52.185
And you're blushing?

19:53.072 --> 19:53.865
Well...

19:58.344 --> 19:59.064
You may leave.

20:07.865 --> 20:08.865
(Chen)
I'm sorry, sir.

20:09.385 --> 20:10.145
I failed.

20:19.472 --> 20:20.690
(Yan's WeChat Moment)

20:32.304 --> 20:33.945
(Jiang Liang)
Love preserved in old film reels

20:33.945 --> 20:35.024
is charming because

20:35.665 --> 20:37.465
it focuses on one person.

20:45.544 --> 20:48.544
Radios and film projectors museum.

20:56.185 --> 20:57.824
(Vespa125 motorcycle)
Careful there.

20:59.744 --> 21:00.385
Watch your feet.

21:00.665 --> 21:01.304
Alright.

21:01.304 --> 21:02.705
Put it down here.

21:15.504 --> 21:16.425
Be careful.

21:16.425 --> 21:17.064
Be gentle.

21:17.064 --> 21:18.425
- What's going on?
- Be careful.

21:18.784 --> 21:19.376
Stop.

21:19.625 --> 21:20.385
Put those down.

21:21.584 --> 21:22.104
Mr. Jiang.

21:22.304 --> 21:23.705
We're changing the exhibits.

21:23.905 --> 21:24.945
We'll finish soon.

21:25.264 --> 21:26.145
Who authorized this?

21:26.344 --> 21:26.865
You.

21:28.185 --> 21:28.705
Put it down.

21:29.465 --> 21:31.905
A collector bought all the exhibits

21:31.905 --> 21:32.985
at a hefty price.

21:33.185 --> 21:34.584
He paid and asked for delivery.

21:34.705 --> 21:35.465
They're sold?

21:36.504 --> 21:38.145
Don't you know I'm your boss's friend?

21:38.544 --> 21:39.865
I pay a fortune for maintenance

21:39.865 --> 21:40.824
every year

21:40.824 --> 21:41.865
just to see these items.

21:41.865 --> 21:42.865
Now they're sold?

21:42.865 --> 21:44.264
What were you thinking?

21:44.425 --> 21:47.024
I-I had no choice.

21:47.145 --> 21:48.584
He paid way too much.

21:48.665 --> 21:49.744
Even our boss agreed...

21:49.744 --> 21:50.256
Who is it?

21:50.744 --> 21:52.104
Who's the buyer?

21:53.425 --> 21:55.064
The heir of Jinda Group,

21:55.344 --> 21:56.024
Shen Haoming.

21:59.744 --> 22:00.824
What are you waiting for?

22:00.824 --> 22:01.584
Start loading.

22:01.625 --> 22:02.145
Hurry up.

22:02.264 --> 22:03.185
Be careful.

22:03.385 --> 22:05.385
You're causing trouble
in this scorching heat?

22:06.104 --> 22:06.784
Faster.

22:08.264 --> 22:08.824
Be gentle.

22:10.264 --> 22:10.784
Hello?

22:11.304 --> 22:11.985
Let's meet.

22:13.465 --> 22:13.985
Alright.

22:28.225 --> 22:28.824
You did this?

22:31.985 --> 22:32.665
Want a drink?

22:35.504 --> 22:36.024
Shen Haoming,

22:36.024 --> 22:38.264
I've never seen you so agitated before.

22:42.665 --> 22:44.225
But your actions are understandable.

22:44.865 --> 22:46.185
You've finally realized

22:47.425 --> 22:49.824
that the money and connections

22:50.104 --> 22:51.264
you took pride in

22:51.264 --> 22:52.425
mean nothing to her now.

22:56.304 --> 22:58.744
Her career is thriving now.

22:59.865 --> 23:01.945
She doesn't need to rely on you anymore.

23:03.024 --> 23:03.784
Meanwhile,

23:04.225 --> 23:05.744
as her partner,

23:06.985 --> 23:08.584
I've supported her

23:09.264 --> 23:10.824
every step of the way.

23:12.104 --> 23:13.304
Not to mention

23:14.665 --> 23:17.024
that your marital bond is crumbling.

23:19.024 --> 23:21.064
Even if our marital bond is crumbling,

23:21.665 --> 23:22.865
as you assume

23:22.865 --> 23:24.344
without any basis,

23:25.625 --> 23:29.024
we are still married, aren't we?

23:30.665 --> 23:31.632
I'm still

23:33.424 --> 23:34.985
her legal spouse.

23:36.344 --> 23:39.064
This is indisputable, right?

23:42.385 --> 23:44.905
If you're just an ordinary investor,

23:45.465 --> 23:47.465
I'd appreciate your support for her.

23:48.104 --> 23:49.665
But you'd better not approach her

23:49.985 --> 23:50.945
with ulterior motives.

23:53.865 --> 23:55.504
I won't tolerate anyone who wrecks

23:56.865 --> 23:58.304
people's families.

23:59.865 --> 24:00.665
Shen Haoming,

24:00.665 --> 24:01.945
how can you be so confident?

24:03.064 --> 24:05.264
You've long been excluded from her life.

24:06.584 --> 24:07.905
Do you know who she is today?

24:11.104 --> 24:12.985
Do you know her business scale?

24:13.465 --> 24:15.665
What's Yan Studio's production capacity

24:15.665 --> 24:17.985
for major products in the coming year?

24:18.304 --> 24:19.344
What's the product matrix

24:19.344 --> 24:20.264
she aims to build

24:20.264 --> 24:21.344
within three years?

24:21.465 --> 24:23.225
How much profit increase
does she target?

24:23.264 --> 24:24.744
Do you know any of this?

24:25.024 --> 24:26.744
Do you know how much effort

24:26.744 --> 24:28.905
she's poured into
establishing Yan Studio?

24:30.905 --> 24:32.584
Thank you for reminding me.

24:33.784 --> 24:36.264
I'll make sure to
learn all these details.

24:42.304 --> 24:43.185
However,

24:44.304 --> 24:46.705
I think you might have
overestimated your importance.

24:47.385 --> 24:49.504
You just happened to be the investor.

24:50.705 --> 24:53.264
Her success isn't because of you.

24:54.344 --> 24:55.185
Without you,

24:56.304 --> 24:59.344
she could have still
accomplished her goals.

25:00.625 --> 25:01.625
And I will always

25:02.625 --> 25:03.945
stand firmly by her side.

25:04.985 --> 25:06.104
Whenever she needs me,

25:06.784 --> 25:08.145
I'll be there.

25:12.544 --> 25:13.945
Your position is not

25:15.504 --> 25:16.465
so irreplaceable.

25:17.504 --> 25:18.504
Go ahead and try.

25:28.744 --> 25:29.465
Mr. Shen.

25:30.705 --> 25:32.104
Mr. Baraikin has made a request.

25:32.705 --> 25:34.504
Jinda Group must undergo three months

25:34.625 --> 25:36.504
of evaluation
before we sign the contract.

25:36.985 --> 25:38.945
No risks or scandals will be allowed.

25:39.264 --> 25:41.465
Then Mr. Baraikin
will confirm the terms.

25:42.665 --> 25:44.945
Can you find a way

25:45.504 --> 25:46.905
to delay the divorce?

25:51.905 --> 25:52.504
Also,

25:53.544 --> 25:56.544
what should I do about
the film equipment?

25:57.465 --> 25:58.945
Store them in a warehouse.

26:00.824 --> 26:01.905
What a waste of money.

26:02.945 --> 26:03.465
Oh.

26:06.104 --> 26:07.584
Buy some cosmetics.

26:07.744 --> 26:08.504
Cosmetics?

26:08.865 --> 26:09.544
For whom?

26:12.064 --> 26:12.625
Someone.

26:14.160 --> 26:15.106
Okay.

26:21.104 --> 26:23.185
Still no leads on Shen Haoming

26:23.544 --> 26:24.625
and Xu Yan's divorce?

26:25.584 --> 26:27.625
They might still be married.

26:28.425 --> 26:29.865
But my instincts at Yanbo Resort

26:29.865 --> 26:30.744
can't be wrong.

26:32.024 --> 26:33.744
Something is fishy between them.

26:34.985 --> 26:36.104
They feigned harmony

26:37.185 --> 26:38.865
just to secure the deal with Baraikin.

26:39.385 --> 26:41.425
Xu Yan moved out
and started her own business.

26:42.104 --> 26:43.824
Divorced couples naturally drift apart.

26:44.225 --> 26:45.504
But strangely,

26:46.145 --> 26:48.225
Shen Haoming keeps
mentioning her at work.

26:48.744 --> 26:49.945
They're still intimate.

26:50.824 --> 26:52.744
He's even visited her rented apartment.

26:55.104 --> 26:56.744
Back at Yanbo Resort,

26:57.264 --> 26:58.385
they put on quite a show.

26:59.945 --> 27:01.145
They're kind of romantic.

27:04.304 --> 27:05.865
Even if they're in a fight,

27:06.304 --> 27:08.185
Baraikin's three-month inspection

27:10.185 --> 27:11.385
will make Shen Haoming

27:11.744 --> 27:13.104
try every means to keep Xu Yan

27:13.104 --> 27:13.985
from leaving.

27:15.945 --> 27:17.185
I don't care what you do.

27:17.824 --> 27:18.665
Use Fang Lei

27:18.985 --> 27:20.665
or your legal connections,

27:21.104 --> 27:24.425
obtain evidence of their divorce

27:24.544 --> 27:26.024
or marital breakdown in three months.

27:27.985 --> 27:28.584
Remember.

27:29.584 --> 27:30.985
Don't let your godfather down.

27:31.504 --> 27:33.225
If neither approach works,

27:34.064 --> 27:36.425
Yan Studio can also be the target.

27:41.185 --> 27:41.744
Enjoy.

27:41.784 --> 27:42.320
Thank you.

27:44.560 --> 27:46.425
- Sister...
- No. I'm not your sister.

27:46.945 --> 27:48.425
You'll remain my sister-in-law

27:48.425 --> 27:49.264
until I'm divorced.

27:49.584 --> 27:51.024
I stand by my sister.

27:51.425 --> 27:52.625
I won't persuade her

27:53.225 --> 27:54.705
to reconcile with you.

27:59.584 --> 28:01.344
I tried every possible way

28:03.625 --> 28:05.744
to make things right with Yan.

28:07.784 --> 28:08.465
Last month,

28:08.865 --> 28:11.385
we were supposed
to finalize the divorce.

28:12.945 --> 28:14.824
I used every excuse to delay it

28:15.185 --> 28:16.665
and missed the deadline.

28:21.705 --> 28:23.104
That was the first time

28:23.744 --> 28:24.905
I avoided facing reality.

28:25.945 --> 28:27.145
It was also the first time

28:28.304 --> 28:30.385
I was so terrified to solve an issue.

28:33.136 --> 28:34.032
Sister.

28:35.744 --> 28:37.264
I don't want to divorce Yan.

28:38.425 --> 28:39.824
I want to win her back.

28:40.905 --> 28:42.945
Why were you so cold when Yan said

28:44.425 --> 28:46.104
she wanted to make things right?

28:46.705 --> 28:47.744
It was my fault.

28:49.185 --> 28:50.425
I was convinced that

28:51.185 --> 28:53.784
she couldn't live without me.

28:55.104 --> 28:56.544
But after we parted, I realized

28:57.905 --> 28:59.264
that I can't live without her.

29:10.425 --> 29:11.744
I might be her sister,

29:12.784 --> 29:14.784
but I can't tell her what to do.

29:15.744 --> 29:17.064
Figure this out yourself.

29:19.985 --> 29:21.145
Just don't push me away.

29:22.744 --> 29:23.264
By the way,

29:24.225 --> 29:26.705
I met with Dr. Yu some days ago.

29:30.304 --> 29:32.064
Why did you meet him?

29:33.945 --> 29:35.064
Misery loves company.

29:39.705 --> 29:41.465
His current state...

29:44.584 --> 29:45.264
What...

29:46.625 --> 29:47.264
What's wrong?

29:52.185 --> 29:53.905
Stop beating around the bush.

29:53.945 --> 29:54.705
How is he?

29:56.985 --> 29:57.945
He's in terrible shape,

29:58.784 --> 30:00.185
barely eating or drinking,

30:00.905 --> 30:01.945
hiding his weakness,

30:03.264 --> 30:04.465
while obsessing over

30:04.905 --> 30:06.824
how to win back your favor.

30:13.744 --> 30:15.625
I-I never imagined

30:16.504 --> 30:18.584
you would hang out with Yu Yiming.

30:21.104 --> 30:22.905
It's like the bottom two students

30:22.905 --> 30:24.544
helping each other out.

30:26.225 --> 30:27.504
You must be truly desperate.

30:34.945 --> 30:36.865
Given your dedication,

30:37.304 --> 30:39.024
I'll give you one more chance.

30:44.544 --> 30:45.744
Yan's been through so much.

30:46.304 --> 30:48.385
I hope you can support her.

30:49.824 --> 30:50.425
Tell me.

30:51.824 --> 30:52.824
Tomorrow's Saturday.

30:53.264 --> 30:54.824
Yan will be working overtime.

30:56.024 --> 30:56.705
Okay.

30:57.504 --> 30:58.185
Thanks.

31:00.336 --> 31:01.456
Jiang Liang will be there.

31:02.480 --> 31:03.297
Huh?

31:06.465 --> 31:08.905
These are the points I'll address next.

31:12.344 --> 31:13.744
Shen Haoming? Why are you here?

31:16.064 --> 31:17.425
I knew you'd be working late,

31:18.784 --> 31:20.264
so I brought desserts.

31:20.264 --> 31:20.905
Here.

31:22.145 --> 31:23.744
How did you know my schedule?

31:24.865 --> 31:25.465
Look.

31:26.024 --> 31:26.905
There are cookies,

31:26.985 --> 31:27.705
pastries,

31:28.145 --> 31:28.665
and...

31:29.985 --> 31:30.945
I'm in a meeting.

31:35.985 --> 31:37.024
Can I observe?

31:43.665 --> 31:44.264
Of course.

31:44.465 --> 31:45.104
Have a seat.

31:45.865 --> 31:46.385
Thank you.

31:49.024 --> 31:49.544
Go on.

31:51.824 --> 31:53.705
My advice is pretty straightforward.

31:53.905 --> 31:54.784
Seek investment.

31:55.225 --> 31:57.625
China has seen
over 44 million new startups

31:57.625 --> 31:59.385
in the past three years.

31:59.465 --> 32:00.344
A new company emerges

32:00.344 --> 32:01.544
every seven seconds.

32:02.385 --> 32:03.625
The one-year survival rate

32:03.824 --> 32:04.784
stands at 20%.

32:05.304 --> 32:06.665
Two years, 4%.

32:06.784 --> 32:09.465
Three years, only 0.8%.

32:10.425 --> 32:10.985
Ms. Xu.

32:12.304 --> 32:15.225
Do you know why
the survival rates are this low?

32:17.665 --> 32:18.824
In my opinion,

32:19.385 --> 32:20.945
they failed to develop

32:21.064 --> 32:23.665
a truly market-approved product

32:24.145 --> 32:25.264
or service.

32:25.824 --> 32:26.425
Of course,

32:26.824 --> 32:27.784
capital shortages,

32:28.024 --> 32:29.304
talent deficits,

32:29.784 --> 32:31.824
market expansion limitations,

32:32.064 --> 32:32.905
and poor management

32:33.145 --> 32:34.465
are also key factors.

32:35.304 --> 32:35.905
Exactly.

32:36.665 --> 32:37.705
For every 100 startups,

32:37.705 --> 32:38.865
there are 99 ways to fail.

32:39.064 --> 32:40.385
But the most crucial issue

32:40.465 --> 32:42.064
is undoubtedly funding.

32:42.584 --> 32:44.425
A new brand's cold-start phase

32:44.945 --> 32:46.145
requires 3 million yuan

32:46.145 --> 32:47.665
in one marketing cycle.

32:48.145 --> 32:50.192
The annual marketing expenses
approach 10 million.

32:50.665 --> 32:51.385
To put it bluntly,

32:52.024 --> 32:53.064
if you want fame,

32:53.425 --> 32:54.385
keep the cash flowing.

32:54.945 --> 32:55.705
However,

32:55.744 --> 32:56.824
besides funding,

32:57.744 --> 32:58.905
another critical factor

32:59.064 --> 32:59.905
is product quality.

33:00.865 --> 33:01.905
A strong product

33:02.024 --> 33:03.665
must evolve with market needs

33:04.024 --> 33:05.465
through continuous updates.

33:06.385 --> 33:08.784
For startups like ours,

33:09.024 --> 33:10.905
the process involves

33:11.344 --> 33:13.185
constant refinement

33:13.304 --> 33:14.385
and trial-and-error.

33:14.905 --> 33:16.385
This entire journey requires

33:16.385 --> 33:17.865
massive financial resources.

33:19.784 --> 33:21.905
Without solid funding,

33:22.385 --> 33:24.705
there is no room for error.

33:25.705 --> 33:27.264
As entrepreneurs,

33:28.064 --> 33:30.824
we must prioritize financing

33:30.824 --> 33:32.264
from day one.

33:33.625 --> 33:35.344
Cash flow management

33:36.465 --> 33:37.665
determines survival.

33:42.304 --> 33:43.264
You're right.

33:44.784 --> 33:46.705
Yan Studio has repeatedly

33:46.985 --> 33:48.504
faced such crises.

33:50.504 --> 33:52.985
But now you have me and Yuanhang.

33:59.024 --> 34:01.744
We can do much more than inject funds

34:02.824 --> 34:04.304
to support your expansion.

34:05.104 --> 34:06.104
In the long run,

34:06.705 --> 34:08.265
with our lead investment,

34:08.704 --> 34:11.584
funding will never
hinder your growth ever again.

34:11.785 --> 34:13.785
Money solves talent acquisition,

34:14.064 --> 34:15.425
brand building,

34:15.425 --> 34:16.624
and development challenges.

34:24.184 --> 34:26.184
Mr. Shen, any objections?

34:30.305 --> 34:32.985
You've listed so many benefits,

34:33.785 --> 34:35.664
but ignored all the drawbacks.

34:36.664 --> 34:37.392
What do you mean?

34:38.865 --> 34:40.504
The internet ventures

34:41.624 --> 34:44.624
have seen so many
capital-driven successes.

34:45.265 --> 34:46.664
It's nothing new.

34:47.144 --> 34:50.345
But even if you
depict investors as angels,

34:50.425 --> 34:54.104
they are not charities

34:55.104 --> 34:56.425
nor wishing wells.

34:57.945 --> 34:59.504
They're investing in you,

34:59.745 --> 35:01.104
expecting a return

35:01.104 --> 35:03.104
that's dozens or even hundreds of times

35:03.144 --> 35:04.745
their initial investment.

35:06.024 --> 35:06.704
Mr. Liang.

35:07.945 --> 35:11.664
Just tell me whether you will sign
a valuation adjustment agreement

35:11.664 --> 35:12.745
with Yan Studio.

35:24.785 --> 35:26.584
Even if Yuanhang requires a return,

35:27.425 --> 35:29.985
it'll be based on Yan Studio's
actual operational performance.

35:30.345 --> 35:31.345
I can guarantee

35:31.945 --> 35:34.825
that I'll prioritize Xu Yan
and her co-founders' vision above all

35:35.544 --> 35:36.825
and ensure their autonomy.

35:37.664 --> 35:38.345
You guarantee?

35:38.385 --> 35:38.928
Yeah.

35:39.345 --> 35:40.544
What about the executives?

35:41.184 --> 35:42.544
What about your sister?

35:43.265 --> 35:44.704
Even if your sister agrees,

35:45.704 --> 35:47.624
the company's Articles of Association

35:47.624 --> 35:48.745
won't change.

35:49.664 --> 35:52.465
We know that you remember
every data point

35:52.465 --> 35:53.825
with photographic accuracy.

35:54.624 --> 35:55.785
Recall for yourself.

35:56.785 --> 35:59.945
How many cases follow this pattern?

36:21.880 --> 36:22.508
(Equity valuation bets)

36:25.144 --> 36:27.945
The investors want you to maintain

36:28.745 --> 36:31.385
annual growth rates of 50 percent,

36:31.785 --> 36:34.504
100 percent, or even 200 percent,

36:34.504 --> 36:35.905
which is abnormally high.

36:37.865 --> 36:38.584
Why?

36:39.985 --> 36:42.224
To gain a higher valuation

36:42.224 --> 36:43.664
in capital markets.

36:44.144 --> 36:45.704
Such performance clauses

36:46.064 --> 36:48.425
will force you
to conduct rapid expansion

36:48.905 --> 36:51.184
or make prompt
and short-sighted decisions

36:51.224 --> 36:52.624
that damage your fundamentals.

36:52.905 --> 36:54.064
But what happens

36:55.945 --> 36:57.385
if targets aren't met?

36:58.265 --> 37:01.425
Your company would be acquired.

37:02.265 --> 37:03.865
Years of hard work

37:04.305 --> 37:05.544
could vanish overnight.

37:07.064 --> 37:09.664
Do you think you'd still
have the right to refuse then?

37:18.064 --> 37:21.184
Or do you want to create

37:21.224 --> 37:22.224
a quick-profit brand?

37:22.865 --> 37:23.985
Something marketable to sell

37:24.024 --> 37:25.704
at peak value for fast returns?

37:25.745 --> 37:26.704
That's not our goal.

37:27.425 --> 37:29.584
Yan Studio never intended to become

37:29.624 --> 37:30.865
a rapidly expanding

37:30.945 --> 37:32.785
copycat business model.

37:33.224 --> 37:34.704
Our true purpose is bridging

37:34.745 --> 37:37.465
traditional culture with modern life,

37:38.584 --> 37:41.704
making Neo-Chinese Style
with cultural resonance

37:42.024 --> 37:45.544
accessible to and appreciated
by broader audiences.

37:46.024 --> 37:46.825
We're creating

37:47.144 --> 37:50.265
a distinct cultural style.

37:51.985 --> 37:52.664
I understand

37:53.345 --> 37:55.425
this process may take time,

37:56.224 --> 37:58.865
but it is worth waiting for.

38:05.648 --> 38:06.345
So,

38:06.624 --> 38:08.544
with your clear positioning,

38:09.624 --> 38:10.905
you must maintain control

38:11.345 --> 38:12.945
firmly in your hands.

38:14.265 --> 38:15.345
Be the decision-maker,

38:16.184 --> 38:17.825
not the professional manager

38:18.265 --> 38:19.385
who works for investors.

38:25.104 --> 38:27.825
You're advising Ms. Xu
to avoid deep capital ties.

38:28.504 --> 38:31.785
But where will funding come from?

38:37.345 --> 38:38.064
Presales.

38:41.465 --> 38:42.704
IP Ecology Matrix.

38:44.584 --> 38:45.385
First, presales.

38:46.785 --> 38:48.345
The brand isn't established yet.

38:49.184 --> 38:52.104
So I suggest you focus on online sales.

38:53.144 --> 38:54.624
Generate cash flow via presales

38:54.865 --> 38:56.624
and maintain liquidity.

38:57.465 --> 38:58.064
Remember.

39:00.104 --> 39:01.945
Only financial independence

39:02.905 --> 39:05.104
guarantees that you retain control

39:05.385 --> 39:06.224
over your company.

39:13.024 --> 39:14.104
IP Ecology.

39:15.064 --> 39:16.785
The essence of the internet today

39:17.664 --> 39:19.865
is standardization first,
and then personalization.

39:21.425 --> 39:23.785
If you develop one or two hit products,

39:24.425 --> 39:26.465
you can expand with other SKUs.

39:26.504 --> 39:28.785
You could even create
your own derivative products.

39:29.345 --> 39:31.745
Then the complete

39:31.745 --> 39:32.745
IP ecosystem

39:33.305 --> 39:34.504
keeps growing stronger.

39:35.704 --> 39:37.825
What you'll own is creativity

39:39.544 --> 39:40.664
and design copyrights.

39:41.745 --> 39:43.064
With these assets,

39:43.465 --> 39:44.985
you'll have better leverage

39:45.745 --> 39:46.985
when negotiating with investors

39:47.704 --> 39:48.825
to protect your interests

39:49.504 --> 39:50.945
and maintain control.

39:59.584 --> 40:02.144
Building your own unique IP brand

40:04.104 --> 40:07.504
is the essence and core advantage

40:08.504 --> 40:09.345
of cultural products.

40:13.945 --> 40:14.945
Am I right, Mr. Liang?

40:19.425 --> 40:20.425
I think

40:22.305 --> 40:23.865
there's some validity to your points.

40:25.425 --> 40:26.064
Thank you.

40:34.945 --> 40:35.865
One final suggestion.

40:37.985 --> 40:39.184
Whether it's me,

40:39.865 --> 40:40.385
Ms. Jiang,

40:41.544 --> 40:42.825
or higher-level executives

40:42.825 --> 40:43.745
offering advice,

40:44.825 --> 40:45.785
listen to them

40:45.785 --> 40:47.224
but don't blindly accept them.

40:48.265 --> 40:49.184
Final decisions

40:50.184 --> 40:51.504
must come from your own judgment.

40:56.745 --> 40:57.385
I see.

40:58.265 --> 40:59.024
Good.

41:15.624 --> 41:17.745
Thank you, Mr. Liang and Mr. Shen.

41:18.305 --> 41:19.624
I'll consider your advice.

41:19.825 --> 41:20.664
Thank you.

41:20.985 --> 41:24.945
Let's conclude the meeting here.

41:34.425 --> 41:35.104
Well,

41:36.345 --> 41:37.865
I'll take my leave now.

41:38.024 --> 41:38.785
- Want a ride?
- Want a ride?

41:39.745 --> 41:41.385
I prefer walking these days.

41:42.624 --> 41:43.144
Mr. Liang.

41:43.504 --> 41:44.425
Please lock up for me.

41:44.425 --> 41:45.064
Okay.

41:57.104 --> 41:57.905
Shen Haoming.

41:58.945 --> 42:00.664
My fingerprint locks the door.

42:02.144 --> 42:03.865
Please leave so I can lock up.

42:08.745 --> 42:09.265
Okay.

42:15.345 --> 42:16.624
Remember this business model.

42:24.905 --> 42:26.305
What nonsense.

42:39.465 --> 42:40.465
Why are you here?

42:41.544 --> 42:42.785
We agreed on a week.

42:44.825 --> 42:46.265
It's already Monday.

42:48.752 --> 42:49.320
Oh.

42:51.345 --> 42:52.184
May I come in?

43:08.304 --> 43:09.024
Have a seat.

43:09.985 --> 43:10.584
Me?

43:20.425 --> 43:21.305
These are for you.

43:25.064 --> 43:26.465
You practice on yourself

43:26.544 --> 43:28.385
for new makeup looks.

43:29.024 --> 43:29.945
But some cosmetics

43:30.024 --> 43:31.425
may damage your skin.

43:33.504 --> 43:34.584
I've done my research.

43:35.024 --> 43:36.945
These are made with safe ingredients.

43:43.624 --> 43:46.584
Your dry skin is prone
to allergies in summer.

43:47.745 --> 43:49.064
This contains hyaluronic acid,

43:49.224 --> 43:49.825
aloe vera,

43:50.184 --> 43:51.024
and ceramides.

43:51.385 --> 43:53.704
It's great for hydration and soothing.

43:53.968 --> 43:54.584
Here.

43:58.385 --> 43:59.544
Your cool undertones

44:00.425 --> 44:01.385
suit pink

44:01.385 --> 44:02.425
and nude lipsticks.

44:03.465 --> 44:05.624
This is 928, Milky Sakura.

44:06.385 --> 44:08.104
This is 302, Nude Bean Paste.

44:08.624 --> 44:10.865
They give a fresh daily look.

44:14.785 --> 44:17.704
This is 396, Strawberry Red.

44:18.785 --> 44:20.345
That's your favorite fruit.

44:23.465 --> 44:25.825
And 564, Clear Peach Glow.

44:26.664 --> 44:28.064
Low saturation, natural flush.

44:28.905 --> 44:29.520
Here.

44:33.664 --> 44:35.144
- And this...
- Okay.

44:35.425 --> 44:35.985
Enough.

44:38.265 --> 44:38.865
Thank you.

44:40.385 --> 44:41.024
But

44:41.825 --> 44:43.345
why did you suddenly decide

44:43.345 --> 44:44.385
to learn about these?

44:47.184 --> 44:48.104
Because you like them.

44:51.745 --> 44:53.945
We'll have more topics
in common like this.

44:54.504 --> 44:55.584
You'll like me more.

44:57.865 --> 44:58.544
Lin.

45:01.504 --> 45:02.504
Have you decided?

45:08.144 --> 45:11.945
I gave you this whole week

45:12.584 --> 45:14.024
to make up your mind.

45:14.305 --> 45:15.584
I've thought it through.

45:16.184 --> 45:17.584
I think all your concerns

45:18.064 --> 45:19.265
are unnecessary.

45:19.905 --> 45:21.544
I've never felt that our degrees

45:21.865 --> 45:23.865
or jobs put us on different levels.

45:24.425 --> 45:25.385
On the contrary,

45:26.144 --> 45:27.624
you came alone from your hometown,

45:28.345 --> 45:29.704
worked diligently from scratch,

45:30.224 --> 45:31.305
never belittled yourself,

45:31.624 --> 45:33.385
and strived to learn more.

45:34.865 --> 45:35.584
I've always

45:37.584 --> 45:39.385
thought that you're shining.

45:44.865 --> 45:45.945
So I'm sure

45:47.024 --> 45:47.785
