45:49.345 --> 45:51.064
I want to be with you.

45:53.024 --> 45:55.504
You're not proposing, are you?

45:57.144 --> 45:58.584
What kind of proposal is this?

45:58.745 --> 45:59.504
Can't you do it...

46:02.465 --> 46:03.825
Sorry, did I hurt you?

46:04.144 --> 46:05.024
Let me see.

46:06.465 --> 46:07.785
Anatomically speaking,

46:08.584 --> 46:10.224
