46:16.184 --> 46:16.785
What?

46:17.265 --> 46:17.785
Where?

46:19.024 --> 46:19.624
The heart.

46:21.064 --> 46:21.985
You scared me.

46:22.024 --> 46:23.504
I thought I actually hurt you.

46:25.144 --> 46:25.825
Annoying.

46:34.184 --> 46:35.345
But it doesn't hurt now.

46:36.664 --> 46:37.905
Because you're in there.

46:42.745 --> 46:45.584
Is this an orthopedic romance?

46:47.544 --> 46:49.184
Did I not express myself?

46:52.345 --> 46:52.945
Lin,

46:54.425 --> 46:56.024
though I'm just a doctor,

46:57.504 --> 46:59.664
I can support you in Jingzhou.

47:01.265 --> 47:03.064
Feel free to do whatever you want.

47:04.865 --> 47:05.785
Decide on

47:07.985 --> 47:08.785
